# RESEND + SUPABASE AUTH SETUP  (one-time, in Supabase dashboard)
# â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
#
# All DartVoice emails are sent via Resend from the dartvoice.app domain.
# Two channels:
#   1. OTP emails â€” sent by Supabase Auth using Resend SMTP
#   2. Lifecycle emails â€” sent by edge functions via Resend API
#
# â”€â”€â”€ DOMAIN VERIFICATION (Resend dashboard) â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
#   1. resend.com â†’ Domains â†’ Add Domain â†’ dartvoice.app
#   2. Add the DNS records Resend gives you (DKIM, SPF, DMARC) to your
#      domain registrar (e.g. Cloudflare, Namecheap, etc.)
#   3. Wait for verification to complete (usually < 5 min)
#
# â”€â”€â”€ SUPABASE AUTH SMTP (OTP emails) â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
#   In Supabase dashboard:
#   Authentication â†’ Settings â†’ SMTP Provider â†’ Enable custom SMTP
#     Host:     smtp.resend.com
#     Port:     465
#     Username: resend
#     Password: <your Resend API key>
#     Sender:   DartVoice <noreply@dartvoice.app>
#
# â”€â”€â”€ OTP EMAIL TEMPLATE â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
#   Authentication â†’ Email Templates â†’ Magic Link / OTP
#   Paste the HTML from emails/email-otp.html
#   (Uses {{ .Token }} placeholder for the 6-digit code)
#
# â”€â”€â”€ OTP EXPIRY â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
#   Authentication â†’ Settings â†’ OTP Expiry: 600 seconds
#
# â”€â”€â”€ EDGE FUNCTION SECRETS â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
#   Set in Supabase dashboard â†’ Settings â†’ Edge Functions â†’ Secrets:
#     RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxxxxxx
#
#   Edge functions that use it:
#     send-dartvoice-email  â€” generic lifecycle email sender
#     send-confirmation     â€” triggered by dartvoice_subscriptions changes
#     notify-contact        â€” contact form notifications
#
# That's it â€” billing.py calls supabase.auth.sign_in_with_otp()
# and Supabase+Resend handles OTP delivery automatically.
# Lifecycle emails are sent by the edge functions via Resend API.

